6px;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.01em\">LEO CLUB<br><span style=\"font-weight:500;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.16em;color:#6B6862\">OF INDORE<\u002Fspan><\u002Fspan>\n  <\u002Fa>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:30px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:26px\" data-nav-desktop=\"\">\n      <a href=\"#about\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#161412;font-weight:600;font-size:15px\">About<\u002Fa>\n      <a href=\"#leoism\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#161412;font-weight:600;font-size:15px\">Leoism<\u002Fa>\n      <a href=\"#leaders\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#161412;font-weight:600;font-size:15px\">Leaders<\u002Fa>\n      <a href=\"#moments\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#161412;font-weight:600;font-size:15px\">Moments<\u002Fa>\n      <a href=\"#reels\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#161412;font-weight:600;font-size:15px\">Reels<\u002Fa>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <a href=\"#join\" style=\"text-decoration:none;background:#FF5A36;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:40px;border:2px solid #161412;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #161412\">Join Us<\u002Fa>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fnav>\n\n<!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->\n<header id=\"top\" class=\"lci-hero\" style=\"position:relative;padding:150px 7vw 72px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center\">\n  <!-- floating doodles -->\n  <span style=\"position:absolute;top:130px;right:8vw;transform:rotate(12deg)\"><span style=\"display:block;animation:floaty 5.5s ease-in-out infinite\"><svg width=\"86\" height=\"86\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M12 1c1 7 3 9 11 11-8 2-10 4-11 11-1-7-3-9-11-11 8-2 10-4 11-11Z\" fill=\"#FFC73A\" stroke=\"#161412\" stroke-width=\"1.1\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\u002Fpath><\u002Fsvg><\u002Fspan><\u002Fspan>\n  <span style=\"position:absolute;top:300px;left:5vw;transform:rotate(-10deg)\"><span style=\"display:block;animation:floaty 6.5s ease-in-out infinite\"><svg width=\"64\" height=\"64\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"#2F6BFF\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"6 9\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fcircle><\u002Fsvg><\u002Fspan><\u002Fspan>\n  <span style=\"position:absolute;bottom:110px;right:14vw\"><span style=\"display:block;animation:floaty 7s ease-in-out infinite\"><svg width=\"120\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"0 0 120 40\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 30C25 8 45 8 60 22s35 14 57-10\" stroke=\"#15A66B\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpath><\u002Fsvg><\u002Fspan><\u002Fspan>\n\n  <p style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;font-family:'Caveat';font-size:24px;color:#FF5A36;font-weight:700;transform:rotate(-1.5deg);margin-bottom:18px\">\n    <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#FF5A36\"><path d=\"M12 1c1 7 3 9 11 11-8 2-10 4-11 11-1-7-3-9-11-11 8-2 10-4 11-11Z\"><\u002Fpath><\u002Fsvg>\n    Indore's youngest changemakers · Est. 1972\n  <\u002Fp>\n\n  <h1 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(48px,9vw,128px);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.03em;max-width:14ch\">\n    <span style=\"position:relative;display:inline-block;color:#FF5A36\">Leadership<svg style=\"position:absolute;left:-2%;bottom:-12px;width:104%\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 18\" fill=\"none\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 12C44 4 78 15 110 8s72-4 87 3\" stroke=\"#161412\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpath><\u002Fsvg><\u002Fspan>,\n    <span style=\"color:#2F6BFF\">Experience<\u002Fspan> &amp;\n    <span style=\"position:relative;display:inline-block;color:#15A66B\">Opportunity<svg style=\"position:absolute;left:-4%;top:-10%;width:108%;height:130%\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 110\" fill=\"none\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M160 8C70 8 14 30 14 56s70 46 146 46 148-18 146-48C304 28 240 8 160 8Z\" stroke=\"#FFC73A\" stroke-width=\"5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\u002Fpath><\u002Fsvg><\u002Fspan>.\n  <\u002Fh1>\n\n  <p style=\"max-width:54ch;font-size:clamp(17px,2vw,21px);line-height:1.55;color:#3a3833;margin-top:30px;font-weight:500\">\n    The <strong>Leo Club of Indore<\u002Fstrong> is a community of young go-getters turning raw energy into real impact — building leaders through service for <strong>54 years and counting<\u002Fstrong>.\n  <\u002Fp>\n\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;margin-top:36px;align-items:center\">\n    <a href=\"#join\" style=\"text-decoration:none;background:#161412;color:#FBF9F4;font-weight:700;font-size:17px;padding:16px 30px;border-radius:44px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;box-shadow:4px 4px 0 #FF5A36;transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s\" onmouseenter=\"{{ liftIn }}\" onmouseleave=\"{{ liftOut }}\">Join the Club <span style=\"font-size:20px\">→<\u002Fspan><\u002Fa>\n    <a href=\"#leoism\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#161412;font-weight:700;font-size:17px;padding:16px 28px;border-radius:44px;border:2px solid #161412;background:#FBF9F4\">Explore Leoism<\u002Fa>\n    <span style=\"font-family:'Caveat';font-size:22px;color:#6B6862;transform:rotate(2deg)\">— it's free &amp; full of fun ✦<\u002Fspan>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n<\u002Fheader>\n\n<!-- ===================== MARQUEE ===================== -->\n<div style=\"overflow:hidden;border-top:2px solid #161412;border-bottom:2px solid #161412;background:#FF5A36;padding:13px 0\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex;width:max-content;animation:marquee 24s linear infinite;white-space:nowrap\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.04em\">SERVICE&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;LEADERSHIP&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;FRIENDSHIP&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;IMPACT&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;EXPERIENCE&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;OPPORTUNITY&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan>\n    <span style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.04em\">SERVICE&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;LEADERSHIP&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;FRIENDSHIP&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;IMPACT&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;EXPERIENCE&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;OPPORTUNITY&nbsp;&nbsp;✦&nbsp;&nbsp;<\u002Fspan>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fdiv>\n\n<!-- ===================== ABOUT LCI ===================== -->\n<section id=\"about\" data-screen-label=\"About LCI\" style=\"padding:120px 7vw 100px\">\n  <div data-reveal=\"\" class=\"lci-2col\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:64px;align-items:start\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Caveat';font-size:26px;color:#2F6BFF;font-weight:700;transform:rotate(-1deg);margin-bottom:8px\">who we are<\u002Fp>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,62px);line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-.02em;max-width:16ch\">A youth movement, not just a club.<\u002Fh2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.6;color:#3a3833;margin-top:26px;max-width:52ch;font-weight:500\">Leo is an official programme of <strong>Lions Clubs International<\u002Fstrong> — created to spark service, leadership and friendship among young people. The Leo Club of Indore has carried that spirit for over five decades, part of <strong>Multiple 3233 G1<\u002Fstrong>.<\u002Fp>\n      <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.6;color:#3a3833;margin-top:16px;max-width:52ch;font-weight:500\">Our 2026–27 theme is still under wraps — <span style=\"font-family:'Caveat';font-size:25px;color:#FF5A36;font-weight:700\">revealing soon ✦<\u002Fspan>. Watch this space for the chapter we're about to write.<\u002Fp>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:30px\">\n        <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:40px;padding:10px 18px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #FFC73A\">🦁 Sponsored by Lions Clubs<\u002Fspan>\n        <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:40px;padding:10px 18px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;box-shadow:3px 3px 0 #2F6BFF\">🏆 Best Club of the Multiple<\u002Fspan>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px\">\n      <div style=\"background:#161412;color:#FBF9F4;border-radius:22px;padding:28px 24px;grid-column:1/3\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:64px;line-height:1;color:#FFC73A\">54<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;color:#cfccc4\">years of service in Indore · since 1972<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:22px;padding:24px 22px\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:40px;line-height:1;color:#FF5A36\">5,600+<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;color:#3a3833\">Leo Clubs worldwide<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:22px;padding:24px 22px\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:40px;line-height:1;color:#2F6BFF\">140+<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;color:#3a3833\">countries &amp; regions<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:22px;padding:24px 22px;grid-column:1/3\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:40px;line-height:1;color:#15A66B\">1.4 Lakh+<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-top:6px;color:#3a3833\">young Leos serving across the globe<\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fsection>\n\n<!-- ===================== LEOISM ===================== -->\n<section id=\"leoism\" data-screen-label=\"Leoism\" style=\"padding:90px 7vw 110px;background:#161412;color:#FBF9F4;border-top:2px solid #161412\">\n  <div data-reveal=\"\" style=\"text-align:center;max-width:60ch;margin:0 auto 8px\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Caveat';font-size:26px;color:#FFC73A;font-weight:700\">the heart of it all<\u002Fp>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,72px);line-height:.96;letter-spacing:-.02em\">Leoism.<\u002Fh2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:1.55;color:#bfbcb4;margin-top:14px;font-weight:500\">Everything that makes a Leo, a Leo — the definition, the history, the pledge and the motto we live by.<\u002Fp>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- tab pills -->\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:11px;justify-content:center;margin:34px 0 40px\">\n    <sc-for list=\"{{ tabs }}\" as=\"t\" hint-placeholder-count=\"7\">\n      <button onclick=\"{{ t.onClick }}\" style=\"cursor:pointer;font-family:'Hanken Grotesk';font-weight:700;font-size:15px;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:40px;border:2px solid {{ t.border }};background:{{ t.bg }};color:{{ t.fg }};transition:all .18s\">{{ t.label }}<\u002Fbutton>\n    <\u002Fsc-for>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <div style=\"max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;background:#FBF9F4;color:#161412;border-radius:28px;padding:clamp(28px,4vw,52px);min-height:340px;border:2px solid #161412;box-shadow:8px 8px 0 #FF5A36\">\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.definition }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ true }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:18px\">Definition<\u002Fh3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch\">Leo Club is an official programme of <strong>Lions Clubs International<\u002Fstrong>, created to promote and encourage service among the youth of the community — developing individual leadership while serving others, at home and around the world. Every Leo Club is sponsored by a Lions Club.<\u002Fp>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch;margin-top:16px\">Today there are more than <strong>5,600 clubs<\u002Fstrong> and <strong>1,40,000 members<\u002Fstrong> across <strong>134+ countries<\u002Fstrong> and geographical areas worldwide.<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.history }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ false }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:18px\">History<\u002Fh3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch\">Coach <strong>Jim Graver<\u002Fstrong> — a baseball coach and Lion in Pennsylvania, USA — and fellow Lion <strong>William Ernst<\u002Fstrong> chartered the world's first Leo Club at Abington High School on <strong>5 December 1957<\u002Fstrong>.<\u002Fp>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch;margin-top:16px\">They coined the acronym <strong>LEO — Leadership, Equality, Opportunity<\u002Fstrong> (later changed to <em>Experience<\u002Fem>) and chose maroon &amp; gold as the Leo colours. In <strong>October 1967<\u002Fstrong>, Lions Clubs International adopted the programme officially. Leos now span <strong>6,500+ clubs in 140+ countries<\u002Fstrong>.<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.india }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ false }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:18px\">Leo in India<\u002Fh3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch\">Leo Clubs in India are organised in three layers — <strong>Multiple<\u002Fstrong>, <strong>District<\u002Fstrong> and <strong>Club<\u002Fstrong>. At the multiple level, a board led by a President (with Secretary, Treasurer, Vice Presidents and Directors) governs the clubs beneath it, elected for a one-year term.<\u002Fp>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch;margin-top:16px\">The <strong>Leo Club of Indore<\u002Fstrong> is identified at the multiple level as <strong>3233 G1<\u002Fstrong> — proudly part of a thriving national network.<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.objectives }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ false }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:22px\">Objectives<\u002Fh3>\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:13px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:16px;padding:16px 18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF5A36;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">→<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.45;font-weight:500\">Give youth a chance to grow and contribute as responsible members of the community.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:13px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:16px;padding:16px 18px\"><span style=\"color:#2F6BFF;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">→<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.45;font-weight:500\">Promote service that builds Leadership, Experience &amp; Opportunity.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:13px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:16px;padding:16px 18px\"><span style=\"color:#15A66B;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">→<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.45;font-weight:500\">Encourage acceptance of high ethical standards.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:13px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:16px;padding:16px 18px\"><span style=\"color:#FFB300;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">→<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.45;font-weight:500\">Develop leadership through real, hands-on experience.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:13px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:16px;padding:16px 18px;grid-column:1/3\"><span style=\"color:#FF5A36;font-weight:800;font-size:20px\">→<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.45;font-weight:500\">Foster international understanding and friendship across borders.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.pledge }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ false }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:20px\">The Leo Pledge<\u002Fh3>\n        <div style=\"border-left:5px solid #FF5A36;padding-left:26px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;max-width:62ch\">\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(19px,2.2vw,26px);line-height:1.38;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#161412\">I pledge of my hands, extended and open to help those in need.<\u002Fp>\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(19px,2.2vw,26px);line-height:1.38;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#161412\">I pledge of my heart, reach for it, and it will be touched.<\u002Fp>\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(19px,2.2vw,26px);line-height:1.38;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#161412\">I pledge of my ears to hear another's outcry, my eyes to see the plight of others, my knowledge to bring a man closer to his dreams.<\u002Fp>\n          <p style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(19px,2.2vw,26px);line-height:1.38;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#161412\">I pledge of myself for the betterment of my community, my state and my country.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.motto }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ false }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:8px\">The Motto<\u002Fh3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:18px;color:#6B6862;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:22px\">Three letters. One way of life.<\u002Fp>\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px\">\n          <div style=\"background:#FF5A36;color:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:18px;padding:24px 20px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:54px;line-height:1\">L<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-weight:800;font-size:18px;margin:6px 0 6px\">Leadership<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.45;opacity:.92;font-weight:500\">Develop skills as a project organiser, time manager and team leader.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"background:#2F6BFF;color:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:18px;padding:24px 20px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:54px;line-height:1\">E<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-weight:800;font-size:18px;margin:6px 0 6px\">Experience<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.45;opacity:.92;font-weight:500\">See how teamwork &amp; collaboration bring exciting change to your community.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"background:#15A66B;color:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:18px;padding:24px 20px\"><div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:54px;line-height:1\">O<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-weight:800;font-size:18px;margin:6px 0 6px\">Opportunity<\u002Fdiv><div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.45;opacity:.92;font-weight:500\">Make friends and feel the real rewards of community service.<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n    <sc-if value=\"{{ show.flag }}\" hint-placeholder-val=\"{{ false }}\">\n      <div style=\"animation:riseIn .4s ease both\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:34px;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:18px\">Flag Salutation<\u002Fh3>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch\">We Salute our National Flag and Pledge our allegiance to the same. Its honour and glory depend upon the zeal and assiduity with each of us will shoulder our responsibility as a good citizen.<\u002Fp>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch;margin-top:16px\">Its glorious history inspires us to put in good work for the fair name of our Country.<\u002Fp>\n        <p style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:1.65;color:#33312c;font-weight:500;max-width:70ch;margin-top:16px\">We declare our unflinching loyalty to our Country. We maintain that its course shall be our course and that each individual amongst us will make genuine efforts to add to its lustre and glory and make our national flag fly proudly and high in the comity of nations.<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fsc-if>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fsection>\n\n<!-- ===================== LEADERS ===================== -->\n<section id=\"leaders\" data-screen-label=\"Leadership\" style=\"padding:120px 7vw 100px\">\n  <div data-reveal=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom:46px;max-width:60ch\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Caveat';font-size:26px;color:#FF5A36;font-weight:700;transform:rotate(-1deg)\">from the desk of<\u002Fp>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,62px);line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-.02em\">The 2026–27 board.<\u002Fh2>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n  <div data-reveal=\"\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:24px\">\n    <article style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #FFC73A\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:18px;padding:24px;align-items:center;border-bottom:2px solid #161412\">\n        <div style=\"flex:none;width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid #161412;background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,#efece4 0 8px,#e6e2d8 8px 16px);display:grid;place-items:center;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:#8a857a;text-align:center\">PRESIDENT<br>PHOTO<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:22px;line-height:1.08\">Leo Aditya Raja<br>Deshlahra<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#FF5A36;font-size:14px;margin-top:4px\">President<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"padding:22px 24px\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#33312c;font-weight:500\">“It's a true honour to lead as we step into our <strong>54th glorious year<\u002Fstrong> — a legacy powered by passion, purpose and people. Our strength lies in our members: thinkers, doers and dreamers ready to take the club to greater heights.”<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Farticle>\n    <article style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #2F6BFF\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:18px;padding:24px;align-items:center;border-bottom:2px solid #161412\">\n        <div style=\"flex:none;width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid #161412;background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,#efece4 0 8px,#e6e2d8 8px 16px);display:grid;place-items:center;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:#8a857a;text-align:center\">SECRETARY<br>PHOTO<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:22px;line-height:1.08\">Leo Hardik Goda<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#2F6BFF;font-size:14px;margin-top:4px\">Hon. Secretary<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"padding:22px 24px\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#33312c;font-weight:500\">“Stepping in as Secretary is a chance to strengthen the very heartbeat of our club. Let's make this a year where every Leo feels seen, heard and empowered to contribute something meaningful.”<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Farticle>\n    <article style=\"background:#fff;border:2px solid #161412;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 #15A66B\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:18px;padding:24px;align-items:center;border-bottom:2px solid #161412\">\n        <div style=\"flex:none;width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid #161412;background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,#efece4 0 8px,#e6e2d8 8px 16px);display:grid;place-items:center;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:#8a857a;text-align:center\">TREASURER<br>PHOTO<\u002Fdiv>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:22px;line-height:1.08\">Leo Divyesh Kothari<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#15A66B;font-size:14px;margin-top:4px\">Treasurer<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n      <div style=\"padding:22px 24px\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#33312c;font-weight:500\">“Every number tells a story. I'm here not just to manage the finances, but to fuel ideas, back the board and help build a year that's worth being proud of.”<\u002Fp>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Farticle>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fsection>\n\n<!-- ===================== REELS / INSTAGRAM ===================== -->\n<section id=\"reels\" data-screen-label=\"Instagram feed\" style=\"padding:96px 7vw 110px;background:#FFC73A;border-top:2px solid #161412;border-bottom:2px solid #161412\">\n  <div data-reveal=\"\" style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:20px;margin-bottom:34px\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Caveat';font-size:26px;color:#161412;font-weight:700;transform:rotate(-1deg)\">always something happening<\u002Fp>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque';font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,60px);line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-.02em\">Live from the feed.<\u002Fh2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#5a4a12;margin-top:8px;max-width:50ch\">Paste your latest reel links and posters in — they show up here instantly, so the feed never goes stale.<\u002Fp>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/leoclubofindore/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;background:#161412;color:#FBF9F4;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;padding:14px 26px;border-radius:44px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;box-shadow:4px 4px 0 #fff\">Follow @leoclubofindore →<\u002Fa>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- reels carousel -->\n  <div style=\"position:relative\">\n    <div id=\"reelTrack\" style=\"display:flex;gap:18px;overflow-x:auto;padding:4px 2px 14px;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch\">\n      <sc-for list=\"{{ reelCards }}\" as=\"r\" hint-placeholder-count=\"3\">\n        <div style=\"flex:none;width:min(78vw,336px);height:600px;scroll-snap-align:start;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:2px solid #161412;box-shadow:5px 5px 0 #161412;background:#fff\">\n          <iframe src=\"{{ r.src }}\" title=\"Instagram reel\" loading=\"lazy\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:600px;border:0\"><\u002Fiframe>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsc-for>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    